name: The dream of freedom
description:
Future Collection is a 3D collection with animation 
This collection is about my mind towards the future and turning thoughts into digital reality

The dream of freedom 
This art is more about human freedom and liberation from all pain That the wind passes through the meadows and you see nothing but light and brightness 
Sometimes passing through the darkness and achieving freedom creates an inner peace In this art, I tried to convey that calmness and make seeing it feel good to the audience

Sample Music, omid kzemi
24fps
